  <brief_title>Transfer From a Point-of-care Ultrasound Course</brief_title>
  <official_title>Transfer From a Point-of-care Ultrasound Course to Diagnostic Performance on Patients - a Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
  <sponsors>
